# MCP GitHub Push Rules

Rules to ensure consistent pushing to the correct GitHub repository.

## When Pushing to GitHub, Always Push To:

- **Repository Name**: `3D-controller`  
- **Owner**: `larvuz2`  
- **Full Repository URL**: `https://github.com/larvuz2/3D-controller`

### How to Ensure This:

1. **Set the Remote (One-Time Setup)**:  
   If not already set, configure the remote with:  
   ```bash
   git remote add origin https://github.com/larvuz2/3D-controller.git